{"tid":1621783,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「法國加拿大夠有蒙面法！」 沈旭暉：人哋有得換總統","createTime":"2019-10-04T14:48:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T04:00:33.000Z","uid":41998,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"43e1126979fb7b78ed92071aec7f7e02cd665059","tid":1621783,"uid":41998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T14:48:17.000Z","msg":"【國際關係邏輯題】<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊：反蒙面法立法為「無咁壞的選擇」，因為綜觀全球各國，愈民主、愈自由的國家和地區也有就《反蒙面法》立法，包括美國、英國、澳洲、加拿大。<br />\n<br />\n-》所以邏輯上，香港的民主、自由程度和美國、英國、澳洲、加拿大看齊前，沒有立法的理由。<br />\n<br />\n「法國加拿大夠有蒙面法！」 沈旭暉：人哋有得換總統<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1468915950163760\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D1468915950163760&d=HXevA6ue1FLA%2Fu9R3J04LgomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=ce003a35\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1468915950163760</a>"},{"pid":"e651590274cdd16c71311cb50b4157b911d176a4","tid":1621783,"uid":290883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T14:59:59.000Z","msg":"正確！"},{"pid":"49836ad1225a6e48e70f88bdb152a33eedbd2d8c","tid":1621783,"uid":41998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:01:12.000Z","msg":"下次有人講，大家識點駁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c45096ab5c7e2b214bf0dbe4bbfe7af3304c689f","tid":1621783,"uid":41998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:22:29.000Z","msg":"人地有民主制度，隨時推翻你都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbbb13a8dae66612a53efd215bb2a0bfa9e4aee3","tid":1621783,"uid":41998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:43:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41295cbaa6509becefc5eaf3f5b9c0eca8118d08","tid":1621783,"uid":41998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:33:16.000Z","msg":"【國際關係邏輯題】<br />\n<br />\n1a. 假如政府真心相信「緊急法-反蒙面法」可以「止暴制亂」，是民心所向，就不會認為法例具爭議性得需要提前疏散政總全體公務員、提前宣佈學校特別措施。<br />\n1b. 假如政府明知道法例會激化局面而依然行事，目的就不是「制亂」，而是「製亂」。<br />\n<br />\n2a. 假如「反蒙面法」真的「獲社會主流民意支持」，日內立法會就復會，完全可以交由行之有效的正常立法程序處理，完全無須使用「緊急法」。<br />\n2b. 假如政府目的只是使用「緊急法」，內容就不可能只有「反蒙面法」，為了「止暴制亂」，只會陸續有來。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥再走出改造歷史的一步，這是一條不歸路。"},{"pid":"5d77306c465c19b47713761d97609c58a06e1097","tid":1621783,"uid":41998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:00:33.000Z","msg":"可以拎嚟做文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}